description.en:
QAO: QualiFied. Autonomous. Organization. is a decentralized governance protocol for smart assets. 

QAO is a purpose-built solution for community-management of Rarechain. 
QAO is used to stake and vote in order to
receive fees generated from Rarechain's API including also Rareswap and Rarepool. It’s main function is to vote for the system's parameters and management decisions.
